Best Kairosoft Game Kairosoft games are special and this one stands above the rest. I loved Hot Springs Story and thought Station Manager was the best of the new ones. I'd played many of their titles, but this has the most charm. The connection I have to the students/school are more meaningful than what I had in the other games (i.e. Grand Prix, Epic Astro, Mega Mall, Oh Edo Towns, or even Game Dev) If this is your first Kairosoft game, know that there is a learning curve. But it's worth it.

I'd love to hear the reasoning on this as it's turned a promising game into a regrettable purchase.
